{{Youmay|the language of the alien species Kaleesh|[[Kaleesh/Legends|the species]]}}
{{Quote|Your crew members are delightful people - for instance, did you know Mistress Kaliyo is fluent in Kaleesh profanities? A rare and admirable skill.|[[Eckard Lokin]], to [[Cipher Nine]]|<ref name="TOR">''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''</ref>}}
'''Kaleesh''' was the official language of the [[Kaleesh/Legends|Kaleesh]] species.

==Known words==
*''Huk''- "Soulless bug" (Used to describe a [[Yam'rii/Legends|Yam'rii]] species.)<ref name="storyofGG">{{InsiderCite|86|Unknown Soldier: The Story of General Grievous}}</ref>
*''Ingmal'' - a hunting cry.<ref name="crosscurrent">''[[Crosscurrent]]''</ref>
*''Izvoshra''- "Elite"<ref name="lord">{{Hyperspace|url=hyperspace/member/insideronline/86/indexp2.html|text=The Story of General Grievous: Lord of War|int=The Story of General Grievous: Lord of War}}</ref>
*''Sheelal''- "Dreamer"<ref name="storyofGG" />

